==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Absentee
<hw>Ab`sen*tee"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who absents
himself from his country, office, post, or duty; especially, a
landholder who lives in another country or district than that where his
estate is situated; <as>as, an Irish <ex>absentee</ex></as>.</def>
<rj><au>Macaulay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Absenteeism</ent>⟦br⟧
